                                <p class="font-semibold">It's not just a logo or a color. It's not a single campaign or a social media post. These are *components* of a brand, not the brand itself. Your club's new logo is a great *part* of your brand, but it's not the whole brand. The brand is built every time someone interacts with your club, from your Instagram stories to your event's atmosphere.</p>
                            </div>
