                            </div>
                            <div class="flip-card-back bg-[#008eb3] text-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center text-center">
                                <p class="font-semibold">Inconsistency. When messages are mixed or visuals don't align, it creates confusion and weakens identity. Think of a campus event: if official posters are polished, but student group promotions are low-quality, it makes the event and university seem disorganized.</p>
                            </div>
