                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-[#ffcd00]/10 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 mb-16">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-[#008eb3] mb-4">Brainstorm Your Next Viral Reel!</h3>
                    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-8">This guide helps you understand how authentic content can tell a powerful story. Brainstorm and storyboard a short reel for Dominican. Use the carousel below to guide your thinking for each scene!</p>
                    <h4 class="text-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mt-6 mb-8">Choose one of the following topics for your reel:</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-left text-gray-700 mb-8 space-y-2 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                        <li><b>Campus Visit Day:</b> Get prospective students to sign up.</li>
                        <li><b>Why I Chose Dominican:</b> Student perspectives on choosing Dominican.</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl"> <!-- Added this wrapper for proper overflow handling -->
                        <div id="storyboard-container" class="flex transition-transform duration-400 ease-in-out"> <!-- This element will be transformed -->
